<http://drug.uk/usage/pregnancy/af72aad3-572e-4715-91da-6cb9bf609d99> <http://drug.uk/model/patientCondition> "Pregnancy" .
<http://drug.uk/usage/pregnancy/af72aad3-572e-4715-91da-6cb9bf609d99> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Monitoring in pregnancy\nMitochondrial dysfunction has been reported in infants exposed to nucleoside reverse transcriptase inhibitors in utero; the main effects include haematological, metabolic, and neurological disorders; all infants whose mothers received nucleoside reverse transcriptase inhibitors during pregnancy should be monitored for relevant signs or symptoms. null" .
